# trading_bot backend

- **Engines:** `trading_bot/backend/src/engine/` — runtime loops, discovery, evaluation, exits, execution orchestration
- **Services:** `trading_bot/backend/src/services/` — provider clients, persistence, telemetry, config helpers

After **`schema.prisma`** or **`create_views.sql`** changes: from `trading_bot/backend`, run `npm run db:generate`, then `npm run db:setup` when the schema changed.

Strategy behavior must stay consistent with [`notes/reference/strategy.md`](../../notes/reference/strategy.md).
